{"tid":380493,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港依家愈嚟愈少好嘅綜藝節目","createTime":"2017-08-30T07:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T22:47:26.000Z","uid":114167,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be1313cfc900991fca27155a94db877ff8ed7344","tid":380493,"uid":114167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:13:41.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post講起筋肉擂台<br />\n就覺得依家冇綜藝節目好睇<br />\n以前無論係自己製作 買返嚟 定 買版權返嚟自己做<br />\n起碼真係好睇先<br />\n殘酷一叮 美女廚房 決戰一分鐘 <br />\n百萬富翁 一擲千金 筋肉擂台<br />\n同屋企一齊睇一齊笑一齊緊張<br />\n依家嚟嚟去去唔係食就係旅遊節目<br />\n請啲拍完劇嘅一班藝員 <br />\n或者本身圍內friend嘅藝員拍套野就話係綜藝<br />\n好懷念以前好多好笑好睇嘅節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nmplus.hk/enterainment/綜藝節目-8個屬於香港人的經典/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2Fenterainment%2F%E7%B6%9C%E8%97%9D%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-8%E5%80%8B%E5%B1%AC%E6%96%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8%2F&d=hOj2yrHBh8ifRT3WMHuv3Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5c71f285\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nmplus.hk/enterainment/綜藝節目-8個屬於香港人的經典/</a>"},{"pid":"e70187452786e213d1f7cc6cb689602ab9c2e3cd","tid":380493,"uid":65144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:35:13.000Z","msg":"旅遊/飲食節目多錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0532c2e335cb1dbd128dde1c14a43c667ac8743","tid":380493,"uid":114167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旅遊/飲食節目多錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d12c1a058a76425df084f7dbe0ed72108841c2","tid":380493,"uid":114167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:41:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"70741024724818c3b7cf883a683c3d44967a4536","tid":380493,"uid":82587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017